'''Omnipotent Battle Leader''' was a title taken by several [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Warlord/Legends|warlords]]. It was also utilized by the reborn [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Galactic Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] of the [[Dark Empire]] to both lure his soldiers back under his command and at the same time keep his identity hidden until the time was right to reveal himself.

